This paper deals with resource allocation in a communication system, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also considers energy efficiency, which is a topic in systems and control (cs.SY). The use of millimeter wave technology is a key aspect of the paper, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and architecture (cs.AR).
